{
  "stem": "2004.5",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "You could see that they were-- they were actually frightened, but they still threw bread at us.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They were sympathetic, and they were Czechs.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And as I said before, our experience with people in Czech, in the Czechoslovakia, was always much more sympathetic towards us than were the Poles.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Now, there were some Poles, from what I understand-- and I heard stories from fellows that I was with-- that Poles did help them.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "There were many instances where the Polish Gentile people did help.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Unfortunately, I've never came across it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But just because I didn't, that doesn't mean that they didn't help.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They did help.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "There were cases where they did help them.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "All I could see is from my experience, the Czechs helped.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "[LAUGHS]",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It gave me great sympathy towards the Czech nation as a whole.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I'll never forget these things because, you see, it is one thing to throw a piece of bread if you have the option do it or don't do it.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Now here, you know damn well you will be hit with a rifle, with a butt of a rifle, and you still do it because you want to do it, you know?",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So it's-- it is commendable.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It is very commendable.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Now at-- on that transport going to Mauthausen, there is one particular incident which comes to mind.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We were traveling in open trains, which made it relatively possible to escape because, well.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "There was a incident in one of the towns-- and I think it might have been already in Austria-- where the train stopped for one reason or another, and one of the young men said he wants to go off to the bushes.",
      "word_count": 43
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He wants to do what he has to do in the bushes.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they let him.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
